        <item>
            <title>Bang &#038; Olufsen 復修 70 年代轉盤唱機，索價 27 萬元、全球限量 10 部</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/06/bno-turntable/mobile-music/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=bno-turntable</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/06/bno-turntable/mobile-music/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 06:35:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動音樂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Bang & Olufsen]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Saint Laurent]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295855</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Bang &amp; Olufsen 聯手 Saint Laurent 復刻經典，推出 Bang &amp; Olufsen Beogram 4000c Saint Laurent Rive Droite Edition 黑膠碟唱機，定價 35,000 美元（約港幣 27.2 萬元）。這款 1970 年代的傳奇硬件經手工精選修復，搭載新世代唱頭與前置放大器，外殼選用珍貴的 Ziricote 木材，全球限量僅 10 部。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295859" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen1-683x580.jpg" alt="" width="683" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen1-683x580.jpg 683w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen1.jpg 1060w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 683px" /></p><p>Bang &amp; Olufsen 最新推出的 Beogram 4000c Saint Laurent Rive Droite Edition 復古設計之中加入現代技術。這款唱盤由 1970 年代的原裝機型精心修復而成，在 Saint Laurent 創意總監 Anthony Vaccarello 監督下，外觀以高雅的 Ziricote 木盒呈現，並融入鋁質細節，彰顯獨特品味。產品保留原有經典設計，更升級音質，搭載新世代唱頭與前置放大器，迎合現代發燒友需求。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295858" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>音質升級亦不遑多讓，滿足當代樂迷的挑剔耳朵。據外媒披露，Bang &amp; Olufsen 早於 2020 年曾修復 95 部 Beogram 4000c，索價美元 11,000 元（約港幣 85,481 元）仍火速售罄。今次將於 Saint Laurent Rive Droite 巴黎、洛杉磯門店及線上平台登場，令人拭目以待。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295857" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen3-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen3-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><div><div class="css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-16dba41 r-1adg3ll r-1b5gpbm r-a8ghvy" dir="ltr"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-a8ghvy">此款唱盤定價 27.2 萬元，瞄準高端收藏家及音響愛好者市場。Bang &amp; Olufsen 選擇修復原裝硬件而非全新製造，既保留復古情懷，又提升技術規格，與市場上追求創新的品牌形成鮮明對比。</span></span>限量發售料將引發搶購熱潮，或啟發品牌進一步探索聯名可能。</div></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295856" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen4-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen4-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen4.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>資料來源：<a href="http://theverge.com/news/624832/bang-olufsen-saint-laurent-beogram-4000c-turntable">The Verge</a>、<a href="https://www.techradar.com/audio/turntables/bang-and-olufsens-latest-reworked-turntable-is-a-masterpiece-of-retro-revival-in-a-breathtaking-wooden-presentation-box">Tech Radar</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/06/bno-turntable/mobile-music/">Bang &#038; Olufsen 復修 70 年代轉盤唱機，索價 27 萬元、全球限量 10 部</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
