        <item>
            <title>消防新設電動車滅火工具，呼籲市民勿自行撲滅電動車火警</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/06/fireman-new-tools-for-electric-car-fire/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=fireman-new-tools-for-electric-car-fire</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/06/fireman-new-tools-for-electric-car-fire/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 05:35:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[電動車]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295850</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>香港消防處宣佈引入電動車滅火救援工具，以應對日益增加的電動車火警事故。據統計，2024 年涉及電動車的交通意外及火警達 48 宗，較前年激增 92%。消防處強調，電動車起火時，鋰電池可能因高溫引發「熱失控」，火勢迅速擴散並伴有爆炸風險，故呼籲市民切勿自行救火，應即時撤離並報警求助。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295897" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030613201-694x325.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="325" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030613201-694x325.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030613201.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲應急插頭可防止電動車無故移動</p><p>電動車火警因鋰電池結構特殊，救援難度較傳統汽油車為高。助理消防區長文家平指出，電池多藏於車底並有堅固外殼保護，單靠外圍射水難以直接滅火。國際研究顯示，處理此類火警或需耗時 4 小時及 15 萬公升水。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295895" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mfile_1794480_4_l_20-694x448.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="448" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mfile_1794480_4_l_20-694x448.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mfile_1794480_4_l_20.jpg 1275w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲應急插頭為電動車模擬充電狀態</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295915" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481454694_1046063887-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481454694_1046063887-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481454694_1046063887.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲防止車輛在突然行駛，對救援人員產生危險</p><p>消防處新引入的工具，包括電動車應急插頭、滅火氈及電池滅火系統，顯著提升效率。據近期訓練及行動數據，消防人員平均只需 2 小時及 1 萬 5 千公升水，便可穩定電池溫度，成效遠超傳統方法。為進一步提升救援能力，消防處已於各分區配備相關設備，並加強人員訓練。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295916" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481989947_1046063920-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481989947_1046063920-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481989947_1046063920.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲電動車輛滅火氈以窒息法輔助滅火，防止火勢、有毒氣體及濃煙擴散</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295896" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mfile_1794480_3_l_20-694x443.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="443" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mfile_1794480_3_l_20-694x443.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mfile_1794480_3_l_20.jpg 1270w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲電池滅火系統</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295917" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481906043_1046063870-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481906043_1046063870-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481906043_1046063870.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲瞬間刺穿電池外殼並直接注水，迅速為電池降溫</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295913" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481951080_1046063850-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481951080_1046063850-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481951080_1046063850.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲高壓噴霧喉筆可產生水霧，覆蓋電動車底的電池起火位置，迅速降溫</p><p>消防處提醒駕駛者，若發現電池系統發出警示、異常氣味或煙霧，應立即停車撤離，並馬上報警求助。即使附近有水源，亦不建議自行滅火，因鋰電池燃燒釋放的氣體及火焰極具危險性。隨著電動車數量持續上升，相關火警事故或仍會增加，預料消防處將持續提升設備及應急策略。同時市民對電動車風險的認知亦需提升，未來或見更多公眾教育活動，防患於未然。</p><p>圖片、資料來源：<a href="http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1794480-20250306.htm">RTHK</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
